# Incident Response Rules

## Doctrine
Follow [[IR Doctrine]] and [[IR Intake Process]].

## Cases
- IDs: `ES-IR-YYYY-####`
- Register in [[Cases Index]]
- Use [[IR Case Template]]

## Playbooks
- Actionable steps with validation and rollback/containment notes.
- Link detections/hunts that feed the playbook.

## Evidence Handling
- Preserve integrity notes.
- No secrets/PII dumps in Git.
- Lab drills should still use professional case discipline.
